# Demo Scenarios

## Scenario 1 – New Alert

Send alert via REST API.

Expected:
- Event created
- Incident created
- Event status = Processed

---

## Scenario 2 – Duplicate Alert

Send same alert again.

Expected:
- Duplicate detected
- Event not created
- No new incident generated

---

## Scenario 3 – Severity Mapping

Send different severity values.

Expected:
- Priority assigned correctly in incident
